{"type":"message","id":"df088822","parentId":"e628f54d","timestamp":"2026-02-25T14:02:00.020Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:31d23ccc-7a5a-4c0c-9c4c-6a1370057b43 task:31d23ccc-7a5a-4c0c-9c4c-6a1370057b43] 详细检查 EvoMap 相关脚本和定时任务，找出报错和时间配置问题。\n\n## 任务\n\n### 1. 检查所有 EvoMap 相关脚本\n```bash\n# 列出所有脚本\nls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-*.js\n\n# 检查每个脚本的语法\nfor f in /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-*.js; do\n  echo \"=== Checking $f ===\"\n  node --check \"$f\" 2>&1\ndone\n\n# 检查脚本内容\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-daily-publish.js\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-bounty-hunter.js\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-a2a-service.js\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-reputation-monitor.js\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-reputation-boost.js\n```\n\n### 2. 检查所有 cron 任务配置\n```bash\n# 列出所有 cron 任务\nopenclaw cron list\n\n# 检查 EvoMap 相关任务\nopenclaw cron list | grep -i evomap\n```\n\n### 3. 检查执行日志中的错误\n```bash\n# 检查最近的错误\ngrep -i \"error\\|fail\\|exception\" /root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/evomap-*.jsonl 2>/dev/null | tail -50\n\n# 检查执行日志\ntail -100 /root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/evomap-reputation-boost.jsonl 2>/dev/null\n```\n\n### 4. 验证脚本依赖\n```bash\n# 检查脚本中的 require 是否都存在\ngrep -h \"require\\|import\" /root/.openclaw/workspace/cron/evomap-*.js 2>/dev/null\n```\n\n### 5. 修复发现的问题\n- 语法错误\n- 依赖缺失\n- cron 时间配置错误\n- 路径问题\n\n## 输出\n1. 所有脚本的语法检查结果\n2. cron 任务列表（包含时间配置）\n3. 发现的错误和问题\n4. 修复方案\n5. 修复后的验证结果\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 10:01 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772028120017}}
